[Malawi joins the list of African countries currently affected by large
outbreaks of measles virus infection. Control of measles virus infection by
vaccination remains a challenge throughout Africa, even in the best
organised countries.

The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Malawi can be accessed at
